  <summary date="2020-12-21T15:27:19Z" status="Introduced in House">Preventing Regulatory Penalties for PPP Lenders Act 

This bill prohibits federal banking agencies from including Paycheck Protection Program loans as assets when calculating capital ratios, deposit insurance premiums, and other asset thresholds for certain small financial institutions.</summary>
